      <item>
        <title>Dash Documentation Browser</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://a1.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple1/v4/78/0d/e8/780de8d5-c51f-3893-bc4d-91411450480e/icon128.png&quot; alt=&quot;Dash logo&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Dash is an API Documentation Browser and Code Snippet Manager. Dash stores snippets of code and instantly searches offline documentation sets for 150+ APIs. You can even generate your own docsets or request docsets to be included.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.macupdate.com/images/screens/uploaded/JPG/40201_scr_uc1.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width:582px;height:260px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Main Features:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Documentation Browser Features&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Snippet Manager Features&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Special Snippet Placeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Homepage: &lt;a href=&quot;http://kapeli.com/dash&quot;&gt;Dash&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
